				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">The initial list up on Lucy is only the beginning of spell development for Omens of war.  (Much of which is being put on hold to address many of the issues listed in the various class threads requested by Brenlo)  There's a number of new types of spells I'm planning on adding, but I'm waiting for some coding functionality to be finished before I can start testing them.  The list that's up there now is just meant to get the standard upgrades out of the way early on so I can devote more time to poke and prod them a bit during beta.  These spells are far from done.
